article.headline: Crawford scores 24, Louisiana Tech downs Florida International 75-68
article.description: — Isaiah Crawford had 24 points in Louisiana Tech's 75-68 win against Florida International on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Crawford scores 24, Louisiana Tech downs Florida International 75-68
article.story: RUSTON, La. -- — Isaiah Crawford had 24 points in Louisiana Tech's 75-68 win against Florida International on Saturday night. Crawford also contributed six rebounds and four blocks for the Bulldogs (18-8, 8-3 Conference USA). Tahlik Chavez shot 5 for 9 (3 for 4 from 3-point range) and 9 of 11 from the free-throw line to add 22 points. Devin Ree shot 4 of 10 from the field and 3 for 4 from the line to finish with 11 points. The Panthers (8-18, 3-8) were led in scoring by Arturo Dean, who finished with 19 points, 12 rebounds and three steals. Florida International also got 17 points and two steals from Petar Krivokapic. Javaunte Hawkins also had 10 points, four assists and two steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
